                             java.util.ArrayList<uk.ac.ebi.pride.model.implementation.mzData.UserParamImpl> userParameters,
                             java.util.ArrayList<uk.ac.ebi.pride.model.implementation.core.ModificationImpl> modifications)
Creates a new IdentificationGeneral object that store details on a peptide identification.

Parameters:
spectrumFileId - the spectra file id (filename or index)
peptideAccession - accession number of the identified peptide
searchEngine - the name of the searchEngine
database - the name of the database used during identification
databaseVersion - the version of the database
sequence - the sequence of the peptide
start - the start index if the peptide
score - the score of the detected peptide
threshold - the score threshold used during identification
iTraqNorm - the iTRAQ normalization values
iTraqUT - the iTRAQ UT values
iTraqRatio - the iTRAQ ratios
cvParams - cv parameters associated with the identification
userParameters - user parameters associated with the identification
modifications - the peptide modifications
